Race.SpecificTitle: Constable -- 2nd Justice of the Peace Court
PW SB Prop #1 -- 5.15 Mills - SB - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Parishwide School District Propositions
Proposition No. 1
(Millage Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall Claiborne Parish School District, Claiborne Parish, Louisiana (the "District"), levy a special tax of five and fifteen hundredths (5.15) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $793,100 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2016 and ending with the year 2025, for the purpose of giving additional support to the public schools in said Parish?

Race.SpecificTitle: PW SB Prop #2 -- 5.15 Mills - SB - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Parishwide School District Propositions
Proposition No. 2
(Millage Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall Claiborne Parish School District, Claiborne Parish, Louisiana (the "District"), levy a special tax of five and fifteen hundredths (5.15) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $793,100 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2016 and ending with the year 2025, for the purpose of constructing, improving and maintaining school houses and other school property within said Parish?

Race.SpecificTitle: School District No. 11 -- 3.33 Mills - SB - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall School District No. 11 of Claiborne Parish, Louisiana (the "District") levy a three and thirty-three hundredths (3.33) mills tax on all the property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $186,500 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2017 and ending with the year 2026, for the purpose of maintaining and operating school houses or buildings and other school related facilities in the District?
